Package paintingcanvas.misc

Enum Hue

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Hue>
      • paintingcanvas.misc.Hue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Hue>
    public enum Hue
extends java.lang.Enum<Hue>

    Colors (besides black and white) are taken from the Tailwind CSS Color Palette.

    Not indented to be constructed directly in the public API. Internally, it's only use is getColor(String)
